<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MyThoughts</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/23c2a211eb.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@100;300;400&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&family=Source+Sans+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" type="text/css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landingpage.css" type="text/css">

  <!-- <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script> -->
</head>
<body>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="relative z-10 pb-8 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl lg:pb-28 xl:pb-32">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"></svg>
        <main class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-7xl px-4 sm:mt-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-16 lg:mt-20 lg:px-8 xl:mt-28">
          <div class="sm:text-center lg:text-left">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
              <span class="block text-black xl:inline">Welcome to</span>
              <span class="block xl:inline special-welcome-heading">MyThoughts</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
              <div class="rounded-md shadow">
                <a href="/login" class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-indigo-500 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-700 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg">Log in</a>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 sm:mt-0 sm:ml-3">
                <a href="/signup" class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-indigo-100 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-indigo-700 hover:bg-indigo-200 md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg">Sign Up</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <img class="h-56 w-full object-cover sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:h-full lg:w-full" src="/img/ponderingperson.jpg" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="background py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:text-center">
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">A better way to express yourself</p>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-white lg:mx-auto">People sometimes have trouble keeping track of their thoughts and the state of their mentality. Here are some of the features of MyThoughts that may help you with analyzing yourself and your mental space.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="mt-10">
        <dl class="space-y-10 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10 md:space-y-0">
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-white">Personal Dashboard</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-white">View all your thoughts through your own personal dashboard.</dd>
          </div>
  
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-white">Thought Creation</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-white">Create personal thoughts and populate your dashboard with them.</dd>
          </div>
  
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-white">Thought Update</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-white">Make changes to your already created thoughts and populate them with new content such as a new description or title.</dd>
          </div>
  
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <p class="ml-16 text-lg font-medium leading-6 text-white">Thought Removal</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-white">Remove specified thoughts if they are no longer wanted.</dd>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>